CSS:
- Chua lam duoc giao dien hoan chinh => met => chan

+ box model: mo hinh hop
Tat ca cac element (thanh phan) (the) => hinh chu nhat

+ noi dung
+ padding: khoang cach giua noi dung va duong vien (phia trong)
	+ padding-left: 
	+ padding-right:
	+ padding-top:
	+ padding-bottom:
+ border: duong vien
+ margin: khoang cach giua element va cac element xung quanh
	+ margin-left: 
	+ margin-right:
	+ margin-top:
	+ margin-bottom:

+ Tong khoang khong gian chiem cho:
	= noi dung + padding + border width + margin

Chrome developer tools: f12
+ computed:
	Viet css: tinh toan het cac thuoc tinh cua element

+ Selector: Bo chon

+ Chon bang ten the:
+ chon bang id
	+ Dinh danh
	#[ten id]
	+ id: chi dung cho 1 element duy nhat
+ chon bang class:
	+ giong nhu id
	+ dung cho nhieu element
	dau .
	+ mot element co the co nhieu class

+ chon thanh phan nho hon:
	+ su dung dau cach
+ Chon thanh phan con (truc tiep)
+ Chon tong hop nhieu dieu kien
	+ Viet lien cac dieu kien
+ Chon nhieu thanh phan:
	+ dau phay
+ Chon theo attribute
	dau [ten thuoc tinh = gia tri]
+ Chon phan tu dau tien:
	selector:first-child 
+ chon phan tu cuoi cung:
	selector:last-child
+ chon phan tu theo thu tu
	+ :nth-child(n)
	+ :nth-child(odd) => so le
	+ :nth-child(odd) => so chan
	+ su dung tham so n:
		+ 3 cai thi co 1 cai do
		+ n la mot so 0 => vo cung
		3n:
			n = 0 => 0
			n = 1 => 3
			n = 2 => 6
			n = 3 => 9
		+ 3 cai thi co 1 cai do => bat dau 2
			2-5-8-11
			
